Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.92,0:00:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,纸牌屋第一季 前情提要....\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Previously on House of Cards
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.33,0:00:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我觉得我们不应该继续了  - 好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I think we should end it.   - All right.
