Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.88,0:00:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好  既然我们把关系理清楚了...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As long as we're clear about what this is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.47,0:00:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以扮演妓女的角色\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can play the whore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.14,0:00:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,听起来是她的收益比较大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sounds like she's getting the better side of the bargain.
