Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.90,0:00:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,彼得？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Peter?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.44,0:00:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,也许他希望罗素自毁前程\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe he wanted Russo to self-destruct.
