Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.57,0:00:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来的话...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then next week...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.65,0:00:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,总统就会提名安德伍德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The president taps Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.69,0:00:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我想成为副总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, I want to be the vice president.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.28,0:00:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你感受了到了吗？胎动？ \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you feel that? The kicking?
