Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.04,0:00:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,“我需要员工而不是母亲  还有  去照顾你的孩子吧”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}quote, "I need employees, not mothers. Go focus on your baby."
