Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:48.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以去车上待着...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We could jump in the car if...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.01,0:03:50.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,在这儿等着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.70,0:03:55.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,-你给议员买生日礼物了吗  -没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Did you get the congressman anything for his birthday? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.39,0:03:59.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,我买了袖扣  银质的  有他的...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got him cufflinks. Silver, with his --
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:01.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们不谈论生日  不送礼物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We don't talk about birthdays. We don't do gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.99,0:04:02.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.03,0:04:05.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,去把袖扣退了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You should return the cufflinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.52,0:04:07.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,道格\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Doug?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:09.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在给你打电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tried calling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.97,0:04:11.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,-我把手机留在...  -我们得谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I left my phone in the... - We need to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.03,0:04:16.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.83,0:04:19.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,克里斯蒂娜  我刚刚跟她谈过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Christina. I just spoke to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.30,0:04:20.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,佐伊...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did Zoe...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.18,0:04:22.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的  但还不止\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. But that's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.10,0:04:23.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们还找到了瑞秋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They tracked down Rachel, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.13,0:04:25.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰西斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Francis?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.33,0:04:29.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,跟我说说瑞秋  她在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me about Rachel. Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:30.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,我控制住她了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have her under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.50,0:04:31.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,答非所问\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's not what I asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.16,0:04:34.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,我送她回家了  不用担心她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I drove her home. We don't have to worry about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.86,0:04:36.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,你当初也这么说斯克斯基女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You said the same about Ms. Skorsky.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:40.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,还有别人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anyone else involved?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:41.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,只有简宁和佐伊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just Janine and Zoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.50,0:04:42.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们在查罗素酒驾的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They asked about Russo's arrest
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:44.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,而且知道他去找过科佩尼科\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and they know he went to see Kapeniak.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:46.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想他们应该就知道这些了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I assume that's as far as they've gotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:48.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,不要想当然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Assume nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.11,0:04:49.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,我去告诉巴尼·豪尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll alert Barney Hull.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.86,0:04:51.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,拿佐伊怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you want me to do about Zoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.05,0:04:52.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,我对付佐伊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll handle Zoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.96,0:04:53.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,你去办事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.66,0:04:54.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,是  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.86,0:05:09.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,我拿走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I emptied it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:12.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,你周二就又老一岁了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're another year older on Tuesday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.01,0:05:14.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,副总统可不能抽烟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And we can't have a vice president who smokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:27.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,你能结束吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you finish?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.26,0:05:28.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.94,0:05:30.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,我完事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.63,0:05:32.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:35.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,没什么  就是完事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing. I just said finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:37.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不想...如果你不想...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I don't want just -- if you're not...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:40.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  随便了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, fine. Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.02,0:05:45.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,佐伊  是我做错了什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Zoe, did I do something that made you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.94,0:05:46.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.98,0:05:51.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,佐伊  你不能说一句完事了  然后就停下啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Zoe, you can't say something like "just finish" and then shut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.57,0:06:02.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,这里很安全  佐伊  我不是他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is safe, Zoe. I'm not him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:12.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,早上好  杰姬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good morning, Jackie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.15,0:06:15.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,早上好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.50,0:06:19.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,理查德·拉塞尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Richard Russell.
