Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:21.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,1963年  《民权法案》\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Civil Rights Act. 1963.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.45,0:06:24.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,不是所有人都能留下美名\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not everyone can be on the right side of history.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:25.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,连林登也曾站错队\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, not even Lyndon for a time,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.85,0:06:28.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,但没有拉塞尔  林登也当不上多数党领袖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but he would have never become majority leader without him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.23,0:06:31.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是没有约翰逊参议院大楼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, there's no Johnson Senate building.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.23,0:06:31.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}有拉塞尔参议院大楼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:34.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  只能委屈他拿一栋总统图书馆凑合了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. He had to settle for a presidential library.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.79,0:06:37.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们都好久没机会聊聊了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So it's been some time since you and I have had a chance to catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.49,0:06:39.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,你的工作做得很出色  杰姬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've been an outstanding deputy, Jackie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.23,0:06:42.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,比你那些老练的同事还高效\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Far more effective than your more seasoned colleagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:44.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,你能建立同盟  必要时还有股狠劲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're a coalition builder, a fighter when you have to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.66,0:06:48.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我  你怎么看自己的前途\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me, where do you see yourself headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.56,0:06:52.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想做众议院军事委员会主席\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd like to aim for the chair of Armed Services.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.63,0:06:54.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,或者众议院国土安全委员会主席\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or Homeland Security.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:56.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,你考虑过进入领导层吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you ever considered serving in the leadership?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.67,0:07:00.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想那至少也得等八...十年了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I figure that might be possible eight, ten years from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.60,0:07:04.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果我说你这一届就能进入领导层呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, what if I suggested that you could serve in leadership this term.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.91,0:07:07.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,接替我  做党鞭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To replace me. As whip.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.58,0:07:11.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,你要接任副总统了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're being tapped for VP.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.10,0:07:12.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,就算是这样吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's assume that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:17.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,-这也说得通  但我做党鞭  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, that makes sense. But me as whip? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.50,0:07:18.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,我只是个第三任女议员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A third-term congresswoman?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.67,0:07:23.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,你的能力有目共睹  而且还参过战\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A universally admired incumbent who also happens to be a war veteran.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.53,0:07:26.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,按顺序也该是韦伯  或巴克沃特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Webb is next in line. Or Buchwalter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.69,0:07:31.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以  你想想这意味着什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So just consider that for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:37.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们会牵制彼此的选票\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They'll draw votes from one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.40,0:07:40.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,我可没说你会赢得很轻松\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, I'm not saying you wouldn't have to fight for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:42.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我愿意帮你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I'd be willing to give you the ammunition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.46,0:07:45.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.14,0:07:53.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.77,0:07:56.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,我关于韦伯和巴克沃特的文件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My files on Webb and Buchwalter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.73,0:07:57.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,你自己看看吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why don't you take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.38,0:08:00.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们过几天再谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll speak in a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.69,0:08:02.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,还有一个关于你的文件夹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, and, uh, there's one on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.66,0:08:05.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,或许你会想先读那个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You might want to begin by reading that one first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.43,0:08:28.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,简宁怎么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What'd Janine say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.57,0:08:30.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,脱衣舞俱乐部还没开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Strip club's not open yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:32.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,你去查科佩尼科的事吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'll look into Kapeniak?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.47,0:08:34.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果他出现  我就能找到他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If he's on the grid, I'll find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.48,0:08:38.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,-送我去地铁中心站  -不去办公室吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Drop me at metro center. - Not the office?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.85,0:08:41.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,我要去找瑞秋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna talk to Rachel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.28,0:08:44.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,她会像昨晚那样否认一切的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She'll deny everything, like she did last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.52,0:08:47.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,她不能否认上了斯坦普的车  你看到她了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She can't deny getting into Stamper's car. You saw her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.98,0:08:51.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,或许你可以拿篇报道她爸爸的稿子给她看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe you send a version of the story, about her dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:53.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,没人会发表的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No one would print it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.36,0:08:55.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,可瑞秋不知道啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rachel doesn't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.01,0:08:58.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,她说"随你便  贱人"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She said, "Go to town, bitch."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.02,0:08:59.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,不会管用的  我得当面跟她谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It won't work. I have to get in her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:07.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,恭喜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.20,0:09:10.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,-我们都替你高兴  -谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We're thrilled for you. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.88,0:09:12.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想亲自跟鲍勃和泰瑞说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wanted to fill in Bob and Terry personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.12,0:09:15.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们快开始吧  我什么时候出发去匹兹堡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now let's get to it. I have to leave for Pittsburgh in what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.91,0:09:16.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,20分钟后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.83,0:09:18.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,帮吉姆冲刺  就要到终点了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Home stretch with Jim. Whistle-stop tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.84,0:09:19.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在形势很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Looking good out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.92,0:09:21.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,的确  但我们还是不想冒险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Very good. But we don't want to take any chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.80,0:09:23.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,接替你的党鞭人选  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, your replacement as whip, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.72,0:09:25.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,鲍勃已经提出了一些想法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bob has already shared some thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.43,0:09:26.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢霍华德·韦伯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I like Howard Webb.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.47,0:09:29.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,韦伯不错  你考虑过韦斯·巴克沃特吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Webb is a solid choice. Have you thought about Wes Buchwalter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.43,0:09:30.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,巴克沃特太冲动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Buchwalter's a hot-head.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:32.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,那么韦伯你觉得可以吗  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, could you live with Webb, Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.91,0:09:35.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,韦伯懂战术  但做事虎头蛇尾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Webb is a good tactician, but he lacks follow-through.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:37.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,巴克沃特是个粗人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The problem with Buchwalter is he's too abrasive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:39.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,毫无魅力  树敌太多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No charm. Lots of enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.73,0:09:40.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,还有别的选择吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is there a third option?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.70,0:09:43.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们是党团资历最深的两位  轮到他们了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're the two most senior members in the caucus. It's their turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.00,0:09:45.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,总统先生  可不可以让党内成员一起挑选\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President, what if we let the caucus pick?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.46,0:09:47.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,大家公平竞争  他们两人都很有资质\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let it be a wide-open race. Both men are qualified.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:49.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,领导层在这事上要意见一致\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The leadership should be united in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.79,0:09:51.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能各自支持不同的候选人  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We don't want to be backing different candidates, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.61,0:09:53.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,那我们就干脆别插手  谁都别支持谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So we stay out of it and neither of us backs anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.89,0:09:54.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,这挺好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.57,0:09:57.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,党团会尊重凭实力竞争上来的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Caucus will respect someone who did it the old-fashioned way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:09:59.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,几位  这事你们做主\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, gentlemen, it's your call to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.98,0:10:02.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们自己讨论决定  然后告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Figure it out amongst yourselves. Let me know what you decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.27,0:10:03.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.24,0:10:07.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,帮我接刘易斯部长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Put me through to Secretary Lewis.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.87,0:10:10.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克  我不想为这事跟你争\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Frank, I don't want to go to battle with you on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.20,0:10:11.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们犯过这种错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've been down that road.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.26,0:10:12.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,说得是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I couldn't agree more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.52,0:10:13.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,公平竞争让我紧张\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}An open race makes me nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.87,0:10:15.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,我只是提议一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, look, it was just a suggestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.70,0:10:18.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,-我再想想吧  -谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'll put some thought into it. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:23.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,我去做做他的工作吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, let me -- let me go work on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.61,0:10:24.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,祝你好运了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.03,0:10:39.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,你来干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.29,0:10:40.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,问我要点什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ask me what I want to order.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.35,0:10:49.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,想好点什么了吗  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you decided, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:52.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,你马上辞职  告诉里昂你不干了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need you to quit your job. Tell Leon it's your last day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.84,0:10:53.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.06,0:10:55.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,表现自然点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Act normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.25,0:11:00.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,要什么配菜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you want a side with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.19,0:11:01.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们能找到你一次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They found you once.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.52,0:11:03.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,不能冒险再有第二次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can't take the chance they'll find you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:04.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,我去哪弄钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What am I supposed to do about money?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:08.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,照我说的做  回家  收拾东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do as I say. Go home and pack your things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.28,0:11:09.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,我十点过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll come by around ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.32,0:11:11.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,-那我就无权决定...  -够了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well -- but I don't get a say in any... - Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.81,0:11:20.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,只收拾一个箱子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One suitcase. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.34,0:11:22.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,-你至少也告诉我...  -我要肉馅土豆馅饼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Can you at least tell me... - I'll take the shepherd's pie
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.14,0:11:24.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,配菜要球芽甘蓝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with a side of Brussels sprouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.17,0:11:26.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,带走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.98,0:11:30.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们不想上法庭  她的律师不想上法庭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We don't want a trial. Her lawyers don't want a trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.77,0:11:32.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,但科尔女士就是不听劝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But Ms. Cole won't listen to reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:34.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,即便如此  如果你再给我点时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That said, if you give me a little more time, I think that --
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:36.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果她想上法庭  那就随她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If she wants to go to court, then let's give her that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.72,0:11:39.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,虽然她现在不肯讲理  不代表将来...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just because she's being unreasonable now doesn't mean she --
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.08,0:11:40.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,我受够了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.06,0:11:41.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,你这是膝跳反应\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's a knee-jerk reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:44.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你不是个不理智不耐心的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've never known you to be a person who was irrational or impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.66,0:11:46.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,我再去找找她的律师  或许我们...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let me check back with her lawyers, and maybe we can --
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.02,0:11:47.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,最早什么时候能开庭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's the soonest we can get a trial date?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.95,0:11:48.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,克莱尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Claire...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.51,0:11:49.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,给我个大致时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give me a timeframe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.25,0:11:52.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,最早也六个月后吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Six months, at the earliest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.12,0:11:58.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,转告她那边  然后就中止沟通\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Inform her people, then no more communication.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.47,0:12:03.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,作为你的律师  我有责任强烈建议你不要这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As your counsel, it is my duty to strongly advise you against this.
