Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.66,0:12:36.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,有事吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.32,0:12:39.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,我找瑞秋·波斯纳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. I'm looking for Rachel Posner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.92,0:12:41.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,她不在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.82,0:12:43.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,她晚些时候会来吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, is she coming in later?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.27,0:12:44.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.73,0:12:45.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,我认识她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.47,0:12:48.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,你朋友可把我害惨了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, your friend really screwed me over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.50,0:12:49.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.77,0:12:51.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,她上班上到一半就跑了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She took off, middle of her shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.59,0:12:54.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不得不去找我的房东来帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had to put my hostess on wait staff duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:58.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,我有点担心  瑞秋有麻烦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, I'm concerned. Rachel's in real trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:13:00.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,我才不管她的私人问题呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't care what her personal issues are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.45,0:13:01.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,我只想知道她住哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just need to know where she lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:02.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们不是认识吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought you knew her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.74,0:13:04.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们认识  但有日子没见了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do. It's just been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.73,0:13:08.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,她给我发短信说她想自残\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And she sent me a text message saying she wants to hurt herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.16,0:13:10.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在又不接电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And now she won't answer her phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:13.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,她有精神病史\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She has a history of mental illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.52,0:13:16.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,你得帮帮我啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've gotta help me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:24.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,我帮不了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.87,0:13:27.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,她的工资和税务报表  上面的地址是个邮箱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Her W-2, the address is a P.O. Box.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:29.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,有什么都行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll take whatever I can get.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.69,0:13:33.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,-我去办公室帮你看看  -谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Let me see what I got in the office. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.56,0:13:36.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果你找到她  叫她别回来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you find her, you tell her not to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.03,0:13:39.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,我才不需要疯子来我这儿捣乱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't need some nutcase creating chaos in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.52,0:13:43.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,-南茜  -是  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Nancy? - Yes, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.87,0:13:44.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,道格回来了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is Doug back yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.91,0:13:47.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,在办公室  还有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In his office. And, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.77,0:13:50.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们开始收到生日贺卡了  还有几件礼物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Birthday cards have started to arrive. A few presents.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.35,0:13:52.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,写感谢信  记录礼物  贵重的...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you notes. Inventory the presents. Anything valuable...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.62,0:13:53.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,摆进会议室\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Goes in the conference room?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.44,0:13:54.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,便宜的...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anything cheap...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.26,0:13:55.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,给实习生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Goes to the interns.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.07,0:13:56.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,你知道怎么处理贺卡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you know what to do with the cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.39,0:13:57.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.52,0:14:07.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,我今晚去接她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm picking her up tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.12,0:14:09.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,我在乔帕都安排好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got everything set up for her in Joppa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.13,0:14:10.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,那是哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.01,0:14:12.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,马里兰  巴尔的摩北30分钟路程\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maryland. About 30 minutes north of Baltimore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.57,0:14:13.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,太近了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's close to home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.86,0:14:16.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们想让她消失  但我们得能找到她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We want her to disappear, but not on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.73,0:14:18.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,-好吧  一次性电话买好了吗  -嗯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Fine. Do you have the burner? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.19,0:14:29.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,生日快乐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.78,0:14:33.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,预付款的  你只要开机拨号就行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's prepaid. All you need to do is turn it on and dial.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.81,0:14:35.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,电话记录还得处理掉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We still have the phone history.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:37.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以日后更要小心了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All the more reason to be safe going forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.74,0:14:39.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,克里斯蒂娜怎么样了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where are we with Christina?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.16,0:14:40.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,我在办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.20,0:14:42.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,安排她去琳达手下  我今早打过电话了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Linda's office. I called her this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.71,0:14:49.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,你是吉莉安·科尔吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you Gillian Cole?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.52,0:14:52.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我们认识吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. Uh, have we met?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:54.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有  但你认识我丈夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, we haven't met. You know my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:14:55.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,你丈夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.88,0:14:57.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,大卫·阿普博姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}David Applebaum.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.52,0:15:00.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,看来是真的喽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:02.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,那只是个错误\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.05,0:15:05.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,你想看看我们的孩子吗  我可以给你看看照片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You want to see our kids? I can show you pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.04,0:15:07.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,阿普博姆太太  我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mrs. Applebaum, I -- I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.07,0:15:08.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,你以为你是谁啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who the fuck do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.33,0:15:09.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.57,0:15:11.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,你抱歉  我觉得你并不抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're sorry? I don't think you're sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.75,0:15:13.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,而且你也休想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And don't think for a second
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.20,0:15:14.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,凭这个孩子来向我们要钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you're gonna use that baby to get money out of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.90,0:15:16.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,他根本不知道我怀孕了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He doesn't even know I'm pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.46,0:15:18.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,但你知道他是有妇之夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you knew he was married.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:19.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么能这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How could you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.70,0:15:21.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,-他说起过我们吗  -没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Did he talk about us? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.29,0:15:24.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,说谎的婊子  我让你难堪了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lying bitch. Am I embarrassing you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:28.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,你想过这对我和我孩子的羞辱吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you think about how you would humiliate me and my kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.56,0:15:32.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,再跟别人老公上床记得戴套\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Use a condom the next time you fuck somebody's husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.88,0:16:01.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,还不到24小时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's been less than 24 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.66,0:16:03.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,她正在上班就突然辞职了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She quits her job in the middle of a shift?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.61,0:16:04.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,她害怕了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:05.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,换了我也会跑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd take off, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.83,0:16:07.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,是安德伍德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.11,0:16:08.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,他行动比我们快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's moving faster than we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.06,0:16:10.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,脱衣舞女呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What about the stripper?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.29,0:16:12.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,不肯开口\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Refuses to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.09,0:16:13.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,科佩尼科呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kapeniak?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.30,0:16:15.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,住址不详  没兄弟姐妹  父母双亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No current address. No siblings. Parents are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.17,0:16:17.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,瑞秋是唯一的机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rachel's the last loose end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.89,0:16:20.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,除了酒驾  她肯定还知道点别的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She must know something else. Bigger than the DUI.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.95,0:16:22.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,知道她去哪了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Any idea where she went?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.92,0:16:26.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,有个杜邦的邮箱地址  但管理员都没见过她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got a P.O. Box in Dupont, but none of the clerks have seen her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.05,0:16:27.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,我可以去那里守株待兔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I could go stake it out, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:29.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,你找过你的人了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you talked to your guy yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.62,0:16:30.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,明后天吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the next day or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.98,0:16:33.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,他会把罗素自杀的警方报告拿给我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's bringing me the police report on Russo's suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.74,0:16:34.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,我尽量多套些信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll press him for more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.96,0:16:36.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,你下一步怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And what's your next move?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.52,0:16:38.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,想想怎么回复这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Trying to figure out how to respond to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.00,0:16:40.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(150,0)\fs13\fn方正准圆_GBK\c&H34332B&\bord0\shad0\pos(175.2,137.7)\frz15.22}周一下午三点  地点你定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.23,0:16:42.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,几个小时前收到的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got it a couple hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.55,0:16:45.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,他是在给你下套\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think he's setting her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.16,0:16:47.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道怎么应付他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know how to handle him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.87,0:16:49.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,他知道的越少越好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The less he learns, the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.01,0:16:50.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们也许能打探到消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We might learn something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.19,0:16:51.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,是他说了算  怎么打探\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not with him calling the shots.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:52.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,地点是我定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm choosing the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.67,0:16:53.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,有什么区别\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As if that makes a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:56.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,我又不会跟他上床  就是谈话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not gonna fuck him. Just talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.93,0:17:03.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,我去下洗手间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna go to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:06.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,-抱歉  我不该  -没关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm sorry. I shouldn't have -- - That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:07.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,有关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.76,0:17:09.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不希望你疏忽大意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just don't want you to be careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.82,0:17:10.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,不会的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I won't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:13.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,你不想有自己的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You want no life?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.02,0:17:19.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,想一个人做三个人的工作吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You want more work than three people can handle?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.09,0:17:20.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,你想找个第一个月\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You want a decent chance
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.07,0:17:22.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,就可能被炒的工作吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that you could be fired within the first month?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.34,0:17:26.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果你感兴趣  咱就接着谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If that tempts you, we can keep talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.32,0:17:27.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,那些都不是问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}None of that intimidates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.74,0:17:30.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,过去九周里我都在管理一个选区\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've been running a congressional district for the past nine weeks
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.62,0:17:32.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,而且没人帮我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with zero assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.42,0:17:33.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,没人选举我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nobody elected me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:34.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,没人教我怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nobody taught me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.96,0:17:37.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,我那么做是因为总得有人来做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've done it because somebody had to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.05,0:17:38.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,罗素的事是个悲剧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happened was tragic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.76,0:17:40.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,可我不会同情你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you won't get sympathy from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.98,0:17:42.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,我没有时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't have time for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.88,0:17:46.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,我要是想博取同情  也不会到这儿来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wouldn't be sitting here if I wanted a shoulder to cry on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.33,0:17:53.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,瑞秋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rachel?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.61,0:18:10.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,走开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.61,0:18:23.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,我说走开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.99,0:18:26.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,收拾好了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you packed?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.99,0:18:28.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,我哪也不去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.36,0:18:31.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,你今天没辞职\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So you didn't quit today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.59,0:18:34.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,辞了  可我改主意了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I did, but I changed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:37.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,这事由不得你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This isn't your decision to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.51,0:18:40.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,我要回去工作  继续住这儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm keeping my job and I'm keeping this apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:42.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.39,0:18:44.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,你答应过  会让这些都过去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You promised you'd make all of this go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.99,0:18:45.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以你得重新开始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you starting over is the first --
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.96,0:18:48.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,我已经重新开始了  不想再来一次了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I already started over. I don't want to start over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.34,0:18:51.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,我也不想你这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wish you didn't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.67,0:18:54.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,滚出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.68,0:18:57.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,滚出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.55,0:18:58.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,小点声\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lower your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.95,0:19:03.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,我杀了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll fucking kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.09,0:19:05.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,动手吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.98,0:19:17.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,只有我能保护你  你还不明白吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am the only one who can protect you. Don't you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.68,0:19:22.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道自己现在多危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have no idea how much danger you're in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.88,0:19:42.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,收拾东西吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Start packing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.05,0:19:53.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,我每年都得问一句\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know I ask every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.77,0:19:55.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,不过生日  像往年一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.52,0:19:59.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以吃顿晚餐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought we could have dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.72,0:20:01.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,除非是去个没人会认出我们的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only if it's someplace where nobody will recognize us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.79,0:20:02.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不想谁走过来...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't want anyone walking up --
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.75,0:20:05.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,我是说在家  我可以做点菜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean at home. I'll cook something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.77,0:20:07.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,不要蛋糕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.79,0:20:08.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,不买蛋糕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.38,0:20:09.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,不要礼物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.22,0:20:10.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,不买礼物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.89,0:20:13.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,那行  诉讼怎么样了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can do that. How's the lawsuit coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:14.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们不会有事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.61,0:20:17.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们打算将您的安保规模\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'd like to increase the size of your detail
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.47,0:20:20.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,增至国家元首级别  从明天开始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to full head of state status, starting tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.02,0:20:21.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,这可不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, that won't be happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:23.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,提前准备总是没错的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's good to get a head start,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:24.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,这样等他们宣布...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so that by the time they announce --
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.93,0:20:27.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,在我彻底失去隐私之前就剩这几天了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These are my last few days before I never have privacy again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.94,0:20:30.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,我要尽量好好享受这几天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I intend to savor these moments for as long as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.48,0:20:32.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是先生  出于安全考虑  我认为...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But, sir, in terms of safety, I think --
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:33.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,在国会表决认可我为副总统之前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Until I'm confirmed as the Vice President,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:33.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}副总统一职空缺后  由总统提名  国会两院多数票决认可  才算生效
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.77,0:20:36.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,安保问题仍是我来决定  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}security is at my discretion. Is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.35,0:20:37.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,理论上是的  但是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Technically, yes. But --
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.18,0:20:38.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,那不就得了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then that's settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.20,0:20:41.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,那好吧  我们等正式宣布\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right. We'll wait until the announcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.47,0:20:43.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,那么  经国会认可后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, assuming the confirmation goes through,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.06,0:20:44.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们就要解决您搬入\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we'll need to work out the logistics
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.66,0:20:46.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,海军天文台的后勤工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of moving you into the Naval Observatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.66,0:20:46.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}天文台地界内的"天文台一号圈"为美国副总统官邸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.92,0:20:48.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,这也不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That won't be happening, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.51,0:20:50.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,议员会继续住在他的别墅里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The congressman will be remaining in his townhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.04,0:20:53.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,但那里没有必要的安保基建\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it doesn't have the necessary security infrastructure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.91,0:20:58.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,那你们就去建啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then you'll need to build it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.76,0:21:00.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,要建防爆设施\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're talking blast-proofing,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.42,0:21:03.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,固定线路通信网络  24小时办公室空间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}hardwired communications networks, 24-hour office space --
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.36,0:21:05.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,有志者事竟成\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where there's a will, there's a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.04,0:21:08.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,我会直接跟你联络  讨论改建计划\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll contact you directly about setting a plan in motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.02,0:21:16.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,你走之前  还有件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And one last thing before you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.65,0:21:19.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,把艾德华·密查姆安排在我的安保队伍里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd like to have Edward Meechum serve on my detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.80,0:21:20.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,他是国会警察\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's Capitol Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.99,0:21:23.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,目前是  你要调他去特勤处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For now. You're about to appoint him to the Secret Service.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.39,0:21:25.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,那得经过加速培训\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That would require an accelerated training program.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.58,0:21:27.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,先生  我们有很多合格的特工\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, we have plenty of qualified agents.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.51,0:21:29.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,有男有女  都有丰富经验\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Men and women with years of experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.14,0:21:30.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,我很期待与他们合作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I look forward to working with all of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.68,0:21:32.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,只要艾德华·密查姆也是安保队一员就行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as long as Edward Meechum is on the detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.78,0:21:34.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,多谢你前来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you very much for your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.97,0:21:36.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.64,0:21:45.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs9\fad(0,800)\fn方正准圆_GBK\c&HFFFFFF&\bord0\shad0\move(239.04,191.52,239.04,164.88,607,1007)}佐伊·巴恩斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.64,0:21:45.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs12\fad(0,800)\fn方正准圆_GBK\c&HFFFFFF&\bord0\b1\shad0\move(237.12,202.32,237.12,175.68,607,1007)}石溪公园
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.93,0:21:45.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs9\fad(0,800)\fn方正准圆_GBK\c&HFFFFFF&\bord0\shad0\pos(251.52,195.84)}弗·安德伍德
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.93,0:21:45.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs12\fad(0,800)\fn方正准圆_GBK\c&HFFFFFF&\bord0\b1\shad0\pos(246.24,206.64)\clip(235,204,241,222)\t(0,818,\clip(235,205,258,222)}我就来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.34,0:21:51.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,南茜  让密查姆把车开过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nancy, have Meechum bring the car around.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.53,0:22:06.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,上一次就是最后一次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, the last time was the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.34,0:22:08.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  但这很重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know. But this is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.80,0:22:11.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,你总想拉我下水  我不干了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You keep selling me that swampland. I'm done buying.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.06,0:22:13.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,再也不干了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No more.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.97,0:22:16.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,掩盖酒驾的事  你说能牵扯到巴尼·豪尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cover-up. You said it went as high as Barney Hull.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.46,0:22:17.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不是那么说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's not what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.43,0:22:18.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,你把瑞秋·波斯纳的拘捕记录给我时...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When you gave me Rachel Posner's arrest file --
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.72,0:22:22.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,我说的是  肯定有大人物干预  记录才会消失\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What I said is that arrests don't disappear without a big-ass wand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.58,0:22:23.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,那可不能当做证据\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That ain't the same as proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.95,0:22:25.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们认为这事牵扯到议会领导层\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We think the congressional leadership took part.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.86,0:22:26.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,我才不关心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.69,0:22:27.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  你关心  我知道你关心的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, you do. I know you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.87,0:22:29.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  我真的不关心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I really don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.30,0:22:30.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,当年你帮我暴露毒品...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When you helped me expose the drug --
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.54,0:22:33.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们不过是拿点小恩小惠的街头黑警\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They were dirty street cops stuffing a few grams in their pockets.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.15,0:22:35.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,这事可不一样  都是有权有势的大人物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is different. Powerful fucking people.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.70,0:22:37.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,黑警就是黑警  你想保护他们吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dirty cops are dirty cops. You want to protect them?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.77,0:22:38.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,我还有养老保险和家人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have a pension and a family.
