Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.50,0:23:35.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,你的手机在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where's your cell?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.65,0:23:37.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,这里  我没在录音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here. It's not recording.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.47,0:23:41.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,你得删掉我们之间所有的通话记录\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need to ask you to delete all of our phone history.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.47,0:23:42.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,我为什么要删掉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why would I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.45,0:23:44.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,我这是在保护我们两个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm trying to protect both you and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.37,0:23:45.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,要坐牢的又不是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not facing prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.63,0:23:50.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,他酒驾不是你替他掩盖的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You didn't cover up the arrest?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.02,0:23:53.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,是不是因为你想让他竞选州长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is it because you wanted him to be governor?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.37,0:23:57.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,不是  他惹了麻烦  我就伸了援手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. He was in trouble, so I helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.06,0:24:00.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,之后他表现出参选意愿  我就提供了指导\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And later he expressed a desire to run, and I offered guidance.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.09,0:24:01.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,指导一个酒鬼吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To an alcoholic?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.40,0:24:04.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,他当时戒了酒  正在恢复中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To a sober recovering alcoholic.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.02,0:24:06.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,你是指望他会自毁前程吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you want him to self-sabotage?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.50,0:24:08.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,当然不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.06,0:24:09.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,他没戏了  马修斯才来参选\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It got Matthews in the race.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.65,0:24:13.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,我愿意支持有上进心的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I like to back people who want to succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.55,0:24:15.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,比如说你自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take yourself as an example.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.37,0:24:17.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,你不过是渔翁得利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You just took advantage of the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.33,0:24:20.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,得利的是马修斯  我没指望能当副总统啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Matthews took advantage. I didn't seek the nomination.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.07,0:24:24.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,罗素死的时候坐在副驾座上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Russo was in the passenger seat when he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.13,0:24:30.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,这话不准确\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's not entirely accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.57,0:24:32.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,我看过警方报告\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I saw the police report.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.13,0:24:34.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,我还直接和警局局长谈过呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I spoke to the commissioner directly,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.05,0:24:37.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,因为我关心彼得  我想了解全部细节\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because I cared about Peter and I wanted to know the full story.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.26,0:24:40.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,那他没坐在副驾座上吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He wasn't in the passenger seat?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.99,0:24:46.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,副驾座的车门开着  他半边身子躺在外面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The passenger door was open, and he was halfway out.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.34,0:24:47.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,警方认为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They think that...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.47,0:24:51.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,他可能中途后悔了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he might have had second thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.88,0:24:55.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果我去问巴尼·豪尔  他会证实你的话吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I speak to Barney Hull, he'll confirm that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.86,0:24:58.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,你什么意思  佐伊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you suggesting, Zoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.87,0:25:00.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,也许有人谋杀了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe there was foul play.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.11,0:25:01.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,要是有任何谋杀的迹象\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If there was a hint of foul play,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.49,0:25:03.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得警方会不去调查吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}don't you think the police would have investigated?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.57,0:25:05.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,就这些掩盖他酒驾的警察吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The same police that buried his DUI?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.57,0:25:07.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,你认为我也脱不了干系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you think I was involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.96,0:25:10.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们之间有联系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's a connection between you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.63,0:25:12.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,听听你在说什么  荒唐至极\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}listen to you. You sound ludicrous.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.47,0:25:13.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,我只是问问而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm just asking questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.89,0:25:16.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  你这是在瞎猜  瞎联系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, you're connecting dots that don't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.22,0:25:19.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,你想让我别插手  装作什么都不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You want me to just walk away? Act as if I don't know anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.43,0:25:21.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,没错  是我替彼得解了围\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, I got Peter out of a jam.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.66,0:25:23.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,没错  我让他去找科佩尼科\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, I sent him to speak to Kapeniak.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.72,0:25:25.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,但除此之外  就没别的了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But beyond that, there's nothing to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.74,0:25:28.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,别怪我  但现在我实在没法相信你的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you blame me if I find it difficult to trust you right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.41,0:25:29.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,信不信随你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Trust me or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.94,0:25:32.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,我很快就要获得认可正式成为副总统了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I'm about to be confirmed as the vice president.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.69,0:25:36.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们的合作关系已经延伸到总统层面了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And our relationship extends to the Oval Office now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.25,0:25:39.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,别无缘无故地没事找事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't step out of the sunlight for no reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.45,0:25:43.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,让我们忘记过去  展开新的合作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's start this new chapter with a clean slate.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.97,0:25:48.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,你回去好好想想  我会联系你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now you sleep on that, and I'll be in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.55,0:25:58.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们先做血液和激素检测\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll start with blood and hormone tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.75,0:26:00.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,结果几天之内就能出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Those results should be back within a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.75,0:26:01.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果结果不错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If they're good,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.34,0:26:04.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们就开始对你和你丈夫进行基因检测\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we'll move on to genetic testing for both you and your husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.60,0:26:06.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,你和他谈过了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you spoken to him yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.18,0:26:09.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,还没有  我想先做检测\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not yet. I want to do the tests first.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.42,0:26:11.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,这周什么时间做都可以\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can do those anytime this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.32,0:26:13.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,我会让我的人跟你这边联络\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll have my office call yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.85,0:26:15.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,差点忘了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I almost forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.65,0:26:17.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,我上网做了些研究\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've been doing some research on the Internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.77,0:26:19.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,网上的话不能都信啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Be careful of the Internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.52,0:26:22.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,我在搜索四十岁以上孕妇的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I was looking into common issues
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.68,0:26:24.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,孕期常见问题时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}associated with post-40 pregnancies,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.70,0:26:25.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,查到了一个药物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and this drug came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.62,0:26:28.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,但没查到什么详细信息  它叫静脉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But there wasn't much on it. It's Cruvenae...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.92,0:26:30.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,静脉雌酮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cruvenae-tenuestrin.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.98,0:26:32.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,你没找到详细信息是因为这种药\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You probably haven't found much because it's,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.71,0:26:34.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,还处在测试阶段\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}still in the beta stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.42,0:26:36.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,这药物有什么疗效\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And what does it do?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.07,0:26:39.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,它能促进血液流往胎盘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It helps maximize blood flow to the placenta.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.01,0:26:42.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,此前还没有哪种药物能做到这一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Until CVT there hasn't been any viable drug for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.34,0:26:44.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,这药目前仍有争议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The jury's still out.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.81,0:26:48.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是各年龄段的女性都可能患上胎盘机能不全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But placental insufficiency affects women of all ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.50,0:26:50.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,你现在先别担心这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wouldn't worry about it for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.70,0:26:53.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们还是按部就班  慢慢来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's putting the cart way before the horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.10,0:27:00.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,马修斯已经稳操胜券\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, Matthews has this locked up,
