Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.26,0:28:02.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你会做出你认为最好的决定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know you'll do whatever you think is best.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.29,0:28:08.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是安德伍德确认了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But Underwood confirmed it.
