Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.55,0:28:33.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,你还会再联系他吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you gonna contact him again?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.16,0:28:35.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.04,0:28:37.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们得放慢进度  退一步重新考虑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need to slow down, take a step back, and reevaluate.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.17,0:28:38.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经让瑞秋溜走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We already let Rachel slip away.
