Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.16,0:28:49.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,除非安德伍德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And unless Underwood--
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.91,0:28:50.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,佐伊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Zoe...?
