Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.83,0:29:05.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,弗莱迪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Freddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.93,0:29:06.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.08,0:29:10.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,今早的肋排是不是有什么不同\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Was there something different about these ribs this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.87,0:29:13.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,更好吃了还是难吃了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Better or worse?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.58,0:29:16.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,我本以为你的肋排是美味到极致了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't think that they could get any better,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.36,0:29:18.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,不过今天的真是不同凡响\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but these were something special.
