Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.17,0:29:25.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,他慢慢地给猪放血\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Slow-bleeds his hogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.86,0:29:27.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,这屠宰方法不合法  但是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It ain't legal, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.31,0:29:29.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不会告诉别人的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I won't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.07,0:29:31.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道还会不会再去他那里买肉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know if I'm gonna go back to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.72,0:29:33.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,我去他的店\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Went out to his shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.22,0:29:34.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,店后有个房间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's got a room in the back
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.62,0:29:35.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,他就在那里杀猪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}where he does it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.71,0:29:37.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,房间是隔音的  里面装备齐全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Soundproof. A whole setup.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.87,0:29:39.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要弄成隔音的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}W-- why soundproof?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.37,0:29:41.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,因为猪叫得太厉害\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}'Cause of how they scream.
