Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.72,0:29:46.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,往它们的喉咙里插根管子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You stick that pipe in their throat,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.31,0:29:49.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,接下来的十分钟简直生不如死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the next 10 minutes is hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.20,0:29:50.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,你的鼓膜都能被震破\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bust your fucking eardrums.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.61,0:29:54.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,人性化的方式是速战速决\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, the humane way to do it is to make it quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.86,0:29:59.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,装作喂食那样提一桶泔水来  然后  砰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bring out a bucket of slop like it's feeding time and -- -- bam.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.77,0:30:02.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,对准后脑勺来上一锹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shovel right to the base of the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.12,0:30:04.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,猪一声也不会吭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No screaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.33,0:30:09.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,博奇同意公开竞争  但他说的很清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's willing to open up the race, but Birch was very clear:
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.94,0:30:11.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果他不能支持谁  你也不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if he can't endorse anyone, you can't either.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.78,0:30:12.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,很公平\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.34,0:30:14.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,你真的希望巴克沃特胜选\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You really want Buchwalter to win?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.90,0:30:17.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,我希望最优秀的人能胜选\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want the best man to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.06,0:30:20.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,谨小慎微的废话  说了等于没说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That sounds like a cagey bullshit non-answer to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.54,0:30:22.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不想插手这件事  泰瑞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm on the sidelines for this one, Terry.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.94,0:30:25.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么事你不插手  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're never on the sidelines, Frank.
