Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.30,0:30:39.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs12\fad(0,800)\fn方正准圆_GBK\c&HFFFFFF&\bord0\b1\shad0\pos(282.24,203.32)}我们能重新开始了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.94,0:30:51.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,克莱尔  你不回我电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Claire. You wouldn't return my calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.97,0:30:54.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,我就回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll be back.
