Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.88,0:31:23.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果雇主不同意  他们就无法恢复\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They can't reinstate it without the employer's approval.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.15,0:31:25.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,你想让我帮你一把\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you want me to get involved?
