Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.68,0:31:57.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,民事罪  不是刑事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Civil. Not criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.75,0:31:59.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,你想清楚了吗  因为等我们上了法庭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you thought this out? Because when we go to court--
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.79,0:32:01.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,六个月后吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You mean six months from now?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.26,0:32:03.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,你还有四个月就生了  不是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're expecting in four, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.88,0:32:06.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,那么你这四个月就没有药物可用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's four months without the medicine you need.
