Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.48,0:32:25.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,但你还有选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But here's the alternative.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.17,0:32:29.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,这家机构  这些员工\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This office, this staff,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.21,0:32:31.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,一年两千两百万美元都给你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}22 million a year could be yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.06,0:32:34.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,净水计划也是你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The CWI could be yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.15,0:32:36.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,你我的恩怨一笔勾销\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you and me, we wash our hands of each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.78,0:32:38.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,你想收买我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're trying to buy me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.79,0:32:41.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  我们初见时我答应给你权力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. When we first met, I promised to empower you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.12,0:32:43.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,我这是在兑现诺言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm fulfilling that promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.46,0:32:44.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,你骗我怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How do I get screwed?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.41,0:32:47.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,不会的  我辞职  你取代我的职位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't. I resign. You take my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.16,0:32:50.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,没其他条件吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No strings?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.03,0:32:51.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}None.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.55,0:32:53.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,民调显示吉姆·马修斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Exit polls have Jim Matthews winning
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.13,0:32:56.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,将以9到12个百分点的绝对优势赢得竞选\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}by anywhere from a nine-to-twelve-percent margin of victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.26,0:32:58.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,喂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.17,0:32:59.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,安德伍德太太吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mrs. Underwood?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.42,0:33:00.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,我是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.12,0:33:02.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,你好  这里是拉森医生办公室\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hi. I'm calling from Dr. Larson's office
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.43,0:33:05.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,跟您确认一下明早十点的血检和尿检\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to confirm your 10 a.m. tomorrow for the blood and urine tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.23,0:33:10.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,我去不了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.15,0:33:12.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果明天不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, if tomorrow doesn't work,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.67,0:33:15.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以重新安排到周四  甚至周一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we can reschedule for Thursday or even Monday--
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.31,0:33:17.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  别给我安排了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I won't be rescheduling.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.69,0:33:20.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,请替我感谢拉森医生的会诊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please tell Dr. Larson I appreciate all her consultation,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.87,0:33:23.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我经过再三考虑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I've put a great deal of thought into this
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.95,0:33:26.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,决定不再进行其他检测了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I won't be pursuing any further tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.78,0:33:27.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.46,0:35:03.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,你考虑过我们之前讨论的事了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you thought about what we discussed?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.18,0:35:07.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,你说得没错  我们是该抛开过去  重新开始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think you're right. We should start with a clean slate.
