Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.38,0:35:30.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们之间没事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are we good?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.87,0:35:31.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.74,0:35:34.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们忘记这些乱七八糟的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And we can put all this other nonsense behind us
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.01,0:35:36.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,互相信任  互相帮助  可以吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and trust one another and continue to help one another?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.26,0:35:38.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,这样很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.81,0:35:41.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,那现在算是抛开过去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then consider the slate clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.12,0:35:43.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,回答我个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Answer me one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.15,0:35:45.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,副驾座的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The passenger seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.80,0:35:47.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,你说罗素是想出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You said Russo was trying to get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.52,0:35:48.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,这没什么奇...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That there was nothing ab--
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.56,0:35:49.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们不是刚刚说好...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought we just agreed to--
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.71,0:35:52.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想相信你  但你得说明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to believe you, but I need details.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.26,0:35:53.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,你有所隐瞒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}More than what you're sharing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.26,0:35:55.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,你想问什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's your question?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.48,0:35:58.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,罗素酒瘾复发当晚  他出席了一个募捐活动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The night Russo fell off the wagon he was at a fundraiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.84,0:36:00.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,麦克奈利癌症研究所...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The McNeally Cancer Institute--
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.17,0:36:01.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,警察报告里全都有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All in the police report.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.60,0:36:06.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,瑞秋·波斯纳当晚也在那家酒店\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rachel Posner was at the hotel that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.84,0:36:08.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,那是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.57,0:36:11.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,罗素被捕时跟他在一起的应召女\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The call girl who was with Russo when he was arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.94,0:36:13.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,我又不知道她叫什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't know her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.34,0:36:16.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,她消失了  弗兰西斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She disappeared, Francis.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.30,0:36:18.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.27,0:36:22.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,别装不知道  我给行李员看了张照片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't act surprised. I showed the bellmen a photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.82,0:36:24.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,其中一个记得见过她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One of them remembers seeing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.93,0:36:26.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,她是个妓女\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The girl's a prostitute.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.33,0:36:28.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,她肯定经常出现在各种酒店\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sure she frequents many hotels.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.58,0:36:30.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,可偏巧那晚去那家酒店吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But that hotel on that night?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.80,0:36:33.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,你这语气像斯克斯基女士似的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, now you sound like Ms. Skorsky talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.67,0:36:36.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,我没和任何人说过这事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I haven't discussed this with anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.91,0:36:38.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想先问你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wanted to ask you first.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.63,0:36:40.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道那晚发生了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have no idea what happened that night,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.76,0:36:42.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,只知道彼得又开始酗酒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}except that Peter started drinking again.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.86,0:36:44.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道有谁在场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know who was or wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.88,0:36:46.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,真希望我在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wish I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.41,0:36:47.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,说不定我能阻止他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe I could have stopped him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.28,0:36:49.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,你知道瑞秋在哪吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you know where Rachel is?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.20,0:36:51.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,相信我的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Listen to what I am saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.61,0:36:53.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,我是想要保护我们两个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am trying to protect us both.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.54,0:36:55.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,谁都有可能问这些问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These are questions anyone could ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.24,0:36:57.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,但现在只有你在问\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But no one is, except you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.93,0:37:00.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,我真不知你想干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't imagine what you're after.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.50,0:37:01.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,我冒了个险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I took a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.57,0:37:05.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,跑去你家  任你摆布\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Showed up at your house and placed myself at your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.35,0:37:10.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,于公于私都跨过了道德底线\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Crossed ethical lines, professionally, physically.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.65,0:37:13.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,我愿意为这些事负责\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I hold myself accountable for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.25,0:37:16.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,这都是我的选择  我愿承担后果\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Those were my choices, and I can live with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.32,0:37:19.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,我也希望向前看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd like to move forward,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.54,0:37:22.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我需要知道我到底卷入了什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I need to know exactly what I was a part of. That...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.52,0:37:26.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,我要确定我没有卷入...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that I wasn't a part of someone's...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.84,0:37:30.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,把话说完\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Finish your thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.29,0:37:35.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,一起谋杀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Part of someone's murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.81,0:37:37.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,天哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.17,0:37:40.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想要相信你  弗兰西斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to believe you, Francis.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.08,0:37:42.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know you --
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.99,0:40:18.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,简宁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Janine!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.35,0:40:28.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,快进来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.16,0:40:28.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,我打不通你电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've been calling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.47,0:40:38.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,进屋坐吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come in. Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.52,0:40:41.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,喝点什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Um, you -- you want something?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.28,0:40:45.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,水  或者果汁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some, uh, water or, um, juice?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.06,0:40:53.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,你要出门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You going somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.05,0:40:56.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,你要去哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey. You going somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.80,0:40:58.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,去我妈妈那里  在伊萨卡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To my mom's. In Ithaca.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.78,0:41:02.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,-什么  -我要走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What? - I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.05,0:41:05.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,不不  不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. No, no, no. No. No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.61,0:41:07.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,-我们什么都没有  -你要放弃吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We have nothing. - Are you giving up on this?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.85,0:41:10.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,这世上只有三个人知道他干了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are only three people in the world that know what he has done,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.82,0:41:12.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,其中一个已经死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and one of them is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.28,0:41:14.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们有证据  卢卡斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If we had anything, Lucas,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.10,0:41:15.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,任何确凿证据\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}any hard evidence
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.13,0:41:18.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕是一个愿意公开的信息源\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or even a fucking quote from a source that would go on record for us,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.75,0:41:19.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,那也好说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that would be one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.83,0:41:22.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,可我们纯粹在捕风捉影  而他不是闹着玩的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But we are grasping, and he is not fucking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.19,0:41:26.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,是你说服佐伊追查这事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You were the one who told Zoe to pursue this.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.36,0:41:27.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,她告诉了我你说的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She told me what you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.50,0:41:30.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,能把你吓坏的文章才是真正重要的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The only stories that mattered were the ones that scared you to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.27,0:41:32.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,这可不仅仅是死亡威胁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, this isn't just death threats.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.76,0:41:33.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是来真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is real.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.43,0:41:36.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,他不知道你  但他知道我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He doesn't know about you, but he knows about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.36,0:41:38.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是在我邮箱里发现的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These were in my mailbox.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.88,0:41:40.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有发信地址\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No return address.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.27,0:41:41.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,他照了她的照片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He took these of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.87,0:41:44.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,还能是谁  你留着吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who else? You can keep them.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.53,0:41:45.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我不认为这对你有什么帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I don't think they're gonna help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.61,0:41:46.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须阻止他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.46,0:41:47.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,变态混蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sick fucking shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.71,0:41:52.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,简宁  你不能就这么逃跑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Janine, you cannot run away from this!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.31,0:41:57.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,我这一辈子从来都找硬骨头啃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My entire career, I have always chosen the tough stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.27,0:41:58.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,我一向无所畏惧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have been fearless.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.53,0:42:01.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,可你猜怎么着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.67,0:42:04.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,我这回真的害怕极了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm really fucking scared this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.99,0:42:07.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,他重权在握\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's got power.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.31,0:42:08.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,他输不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's got a lot to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.63,0:42:09.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在他完全占了上风\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And right now he is winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.90,0:42:10.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,拜托  我需要你帮助  别这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please, I need your help. Please, don't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.92,0:42:12.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,别做梦了  卢卡斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just wake the fuck up, Lucas!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.91,0:42:34.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,事故发生于昨晚八点左右\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The incident occurred at approximately eight p.m. last night
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.62,0:42:38.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,在大教堂高地地铁站北向的列车轨道上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}on the northbound tracks of the Cathedral Heights metro station.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.29,0:42:40.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,华盛顿特区警察已经判定是一起意外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}D.C. Police have ruled the death an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.31,0:42:41.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(98.4,185.04)\clip(73,185,129,200)\t(819,896,\clip(115,183,124,201)}{\fn方正大黑_GBK\fs14\b1\bord0\shad0\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H080809&}佐伊·巴恩斯
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.31,0:42:41.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(149.76,213.84)\clip(134,213,169,226)\t(1236,1362,\clip(157,210,168,228)}{\fn方正大黑_GBK\fs13\b1\bord0\shad0\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H1C1B18&} 地铁悲剧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.31,0:42:42.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(219.84,229.68)\clip(185,226,264,245)\t(1612,1987,\clip(211,225,264,245)}{\fn方正准圆_GBK\fs11\b1\bord0\shad0\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H1C1B18&}新闻界对事故表示哀悼
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.77,0:42:43.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,佐伊·巴恩斯是头条网的资深撰稿人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Zoe Barnes was a senior contributor at slugline.com.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.56,0:42:51.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(98.4,185.04)\clip(69,173,76,203)\t(0,404,\clip(69,178,128,203)}{\fn方正大黑_GBK\fs14\b1\bord0\shad0\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H080809&}{\blur0\t(2641,3073,\blur4}佐伊·巴恩斯
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.11,0:42:43.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(149.76,213.84)\clip(130,212,137,226)\t(0,563,\clip(130,212,151,226)}{\fn方正大黑_GBK\fs13\b1\bord0\shad0\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H1C1B18&} 地铁悲剧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.44,0:42:51.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(219.84,229.68)\clip(213,223,259,248)}{\fn方正准圆_GBK\fs11\b1\bord0\shad0\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H1C1B18&}{\blur0\t(1859,2066,\blur4}新闻界对事故表示哀悼
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.11,0:42:44.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(149.76,213.84)\clip(130,212,151,226)\t(20,200,\clip(130,212,139,226)}{\fn方正大黑_GBK\fs13\b1\bord0\shad0\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H1C1B18&} 地铁悲剧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.57,0:42:47.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,此前她曾在《华盛顿先驱报》\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Previously she worked at the Washington Herald
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.08,0:42:49.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,做都市新闻记者和政治记者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as a metro reporter and political correspondent.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.00,0:42:52.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,巴恩斯报道过多条重要新闻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Barnes broke several major stories,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.22,0:42:55.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,包括教育改革法案的草案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}include an early draft of the Education Reform and Achievement Act,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.94,0:42:58.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,以及导致迈克尔·科恩参议员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as well as a college newspaper article
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.02,0:43:00.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,未能被提名国务卿的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that derailed Senator Michael Kern's
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.46,0:43:02.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,一篇公报社论\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}nomination for Secretary of State...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.33,0:43:25.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得那些文件怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What'd you think of the files?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.26,0:43:27.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,有不少可以下手的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's plenty to work with.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.46,0:43:28.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,你看了自己的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you look at your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.04,0:43:30.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,里面什么都没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There was nothing there.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.53,0:43:33.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,里面该有什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Should there be?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.37,0:43:35.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,不应该\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.45,0:43:37.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,即便你在撒谎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even if you're lying,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.28,0:43:38.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我现在什么也没找到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the fact that I haven't been able to find anything
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.86,0:43:41.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,这说明你很擅长隐藏踪迹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}tells me you're very good at covering your tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.49,0:43:44.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,这点对我来说很宝贵  这里就是我们的战场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's, uh, valuable to me. Here's our battleground.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.48,0:43:46.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,113票\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}113 votes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.00,0:43:48.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,看来你已经掌握大致情况了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have the skeletons.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.94,0:43:54.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果我失败了  他们不会放过我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I lose, they'll come after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.28,0:43:56.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是你必须承担的风险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's a risk you have to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.90,0:44:00.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么知道你不是在利用我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How do I know you're not just using me?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.30,0:44:02.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,为别人竞选制造障碍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Throwing a wrench into someone else's bid?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.24,0:44:06.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,那是另一种风险  你也可以选择等上十年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's another risk. The alternative is you wait 10 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.15,0:44:08.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,你选我肯定是有原因的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You chose me for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.89,0:44:11.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想知道是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd like to know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.66,0:44:13.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.63,0:44:17.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,你发起过多少次导弹攻击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How many missile strikes did you launch?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.87,0:44:19.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,多到让我整夜不能安睡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Enough to keep me awake at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.33,0:44:20.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,但你还是那么做了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you did it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.52,0:44:21.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的  没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.50,0:44:22.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,会伤及多少妇女儿童\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How many women and children?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.99,0:44:23.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,太多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Too many.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.14,0:44:25.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,就算知道会伤及无辜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you launched those missiles
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.21,0:44:27.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,你还是义无反顾地发射了导弹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}knowing all those innocent people would die.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.11,0:44:29.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,我是奉命歼灭敌人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had orders to eliminate the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.22,0:44:31.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,而你专业高效地完成了任务\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which you carried out expertly and efficiently.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.23,0:44:34.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,你杀过人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you ever killed anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.34,0:44:37.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.38,0:44:40.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,我曾亲眼目睹整栋大楼  整个村庄荡然无存\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I watched apartment buildings, entire villages gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.28,0:44:42.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,就像不曾存在过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}like they were never there.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.47,0:44:45.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果可以  我不想再谈这个话题了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd prefer not to talk about it, if that's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.70,0:44:49.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,你完成需要完成的任务\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You did what needed to be done,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.00,0:44:51.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我选择你的原因  杰姬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and that's why I chose you, Jackie.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.75,0:44:55.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,服役背景  历史清白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Service background. Clean history.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.69,0:44:57.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,上相  我全都看好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Photogenic. The whole package.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.48,0:44:59.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,但更重要的是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But more importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.67,0:45:04.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,坚决  务实\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}ruthless pragmatism.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.36,0:45:07.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们能合作吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are we working together or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.73,0:45:12.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,有公开或私下表示支持巴克沃特的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Any public or private endorsements for Buchwalter,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.31,0:45:13.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,我支持韦伯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I come out for Webb.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.25,0:45:15.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不参与争论  我向你保证\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll stay out of the fray. I give you my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.41,0:45:16.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,你也一样  泰瑞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Same goes for you, Terry.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.87,0:45:23.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢  克里斯蒂娜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Christina.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.02,0:45:27.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,先生们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.77,0:45:30.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,总统先生  宾州情况怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President. How was Pennsylvania?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.27,0:45:55.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢印度菜吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You like Indian?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.73,0:46:18.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,先生  我看到新闻了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir? I've seen the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.04,0:46:22.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道她跟您很亲近\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know she was close to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.64,0:46:27.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,可怕的悲剧啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Terrible tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.90,0:46:31.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,今天特别探员洛克兰来找过我  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Spoke to Special Agent Rockland today, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.83,0:46:33.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,我下周开始培训\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I begin my training next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.20,0:46:35.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.91,0:46:42.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道已经晚了一天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know it's a day late.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.35,0:46:43.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,但愿这样不失妥当\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hope it isn't inappropriate,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.51,0:46:45.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想给您这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I wanted to give you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.43,0:46:52.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢  密查姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Meechum.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.30,0:47:04.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,艾德华真是太贴心了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That was very nice of Edward.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.20,0:47:06.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,他不该为我花这种钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He shouldn't have spent this sorta money on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.20,0:47:08.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,我在楼下开了酒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've opened some wine downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.87,0:47:10.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,我就下去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll be down in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.02,0:47:16.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,你以为我把你忘了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you think I'd forgotten you?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.40,0:47:20.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,也许你希望我已经忘了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps you hoped I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.64,0:47:23.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,别浪费时间哀悼巴恩斯小姐了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't waste a breath mourning Ms. Barnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.04,0:47:25.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,每只小猫都会长大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Every kitten grows up to be a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.37,0:47:27.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,一开始看起来都很无害\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They seem so harmless at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.37,0:47:30.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,幼小  安静  舔着浅盘里的牛奶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Small, quiet, lapping up their saucer of milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.00,0:47:34.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,但爪子一旦长长了  猫就会挠人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But once their claws get long enough, they draw blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.99,0:47:37.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,有时甚至会挠养猫人的手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sometimes from the hand that feeds them.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.64,0:47:40.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,对于我们这些爬向食物链顶端的人来说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For those of us climbing to the top of the food chain,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.80,0:47:42.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,决不能心慈手软\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}there can be no mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.83,0:47:47.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,只有一条规则  不做猎人  便为猎物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is but one rule: hunt or be hunted.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.02,0:47:50.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Welcome back.
